Kanske en instinkt berättar dem att det här är en skärningsskärning.

25
00:02:45,611 --> 00:02:47,834
Scenen är en av industriell aktivitet.

26
00:02:47,873 --> 00:02:50,955
Med hjälp av tågmachiner och tågkommor och kuttare, tåg efter tåg är nöjda av sin fris.

27
00:02:50,974 --> 00:02:52,496
Skärarna arbetar systematiskt.

28
00:02:57,967 --> 00:03:07,252
Operering the clippers with remarkable deftness and skill and removing the whole fleece without injuring it.

29
00:03:07,272 --> 00:03:09,213
They certainly live up to the barbers slogan.

30
00:03:09,253 --> 00:03:10,915
You're next.

31
00:03:10,936 --> 00:03:11,616
No waiting.

32
00:03:14,018 --> 00:03:23,764
Although it has been recorded that as many as 330 sheep have been shorn by one shearer in a working day of eight and a half hours the average tally is from 120 to 150 sheep per man.

33
00:03:41,427 --> 00:03:47,891
Deprived of his fleecy covering, the transformed and bewildered sheep is put with his denuded fellows and is subjected to further humiliation by being branded.

34
00:04:08,490 --> 00:04:11,431
Skäven stannar i paddocken för en vecka eller två efter skäringen.

35
